{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"vue-grid---detail-row\"><a href=\"#vue-grid---detail-row\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vue Grid - Detail Row</h1>\n<p>The \"Detail Row\" feature displays data row details on an expandable pane. The pane can be expanded and collapsed either programmatically or via the Grid's UI.</p>\n<h2 id=\"related-plugins\"><a href=\"#related-plugins\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related Plugins</h2>\n<p>The \"Detail Row\" feature requires the following plugins:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/row-detail-state.md\">DxRowDetailState</a> - controls the detail rows' expanded status</li>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/table-row-detail.md\">DxTableRowDetail</a> - renders detail rows</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note that the <a href=\"./plugin-overview.md#plugin-order\">plugin order</a> is important.</p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-setup\"><a href=\"#basic-setup\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic Setup</h2>\n<p>Add the required plugins listed above to the Grid and specify the detail row component via the <code>DxTableRowDetail</code> plugin's <code>contentComponent</code> property to set up a simple Grid with detail rows.</p>\n<p>Specify an array of the expanded row IDs using the <code>DxRowDetailState</code> plugin's <code>expandedRowIds</code> property and subscribe to the <code>update:expandedRowIds</code> event. Use the <code>.sync</code> modifier for two-way binding.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"grid-detail-row/basic\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>","fields":{"technology":"vue/grid","section":"docs"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"vue/grid/docs/guides/detail-row/"}}